title: UK to spend extra £5bn on military to counter intensifying threats from China and Russia
description: The UK will spend an extra £5bn on its military and aim to lift defence spending to 2.5% of GDP as part of an updated strategy to counter intensifying threats from China and Russia.

title: Dozens feared dead as migrant boat capsizes in Mediterranean
description: Dozens of people are feared dead in the Mediterranean, according to two rescue charities, after a boat that migrants had been travelling in from Libya capsized in bad weather.

title: Pro-Western former Georgian president 'close to death' after alleged prison poisoning
description: The former president of Georgia Mikheil Saakashvili has told Sky News he is approaching death in the hospital he has been moved to from jail.

title: Eight people killed as two boats capsize off coast of San Diego
description: Eight people have died after two boats capsized off the coast of California, emergency officials have said.

title: Rapper dies aged 28 after 'collapsing on stage at festival'
description: A 28-year-old rapper has died after reportedly collapsing while performing on stage in South Africa.

title: India government in stand-off with campaigners over same-sex marriage recognition - reports
description: The Indian government is pushing back on an attempt by campaigners to win legal recognition for same-sex marriage, according to reports.

title: Huge seaweed bloom that can be seen from space threatening beaches in Gulf of Mexico and Caribbean
description: A vast blanket of seaweed about 5,000 miles across is threatening beaches along the Gulf of Mexico and the Caribbean.

title: From frontline to Oscars red carpet: Ukrainian producer swaps body armour for black tie
description: Do you like movies? I do, but sometimes real life is even crazier than the movies.

title: Mystery of sisters and friend missing in Mexico - as Texas says country 'too dangerous to travel to'
description: Two Texas sisters and their friend have not been heard from for about two weeks after going missing in Mexico.

title: Rishi Sunak hails UK's alliances as 'source of strength' ahead of submarines meeting
description: Rishi Sunak has hailed the UK's global alliances as its "greatest source of strength and security" as he prepared to meet Joe Biden to flesh out a major defence deal.

title: Israel says three Palestinian gunmen shot dead after opening fire on soldiers in West Bank
description: The Israeli army says its soldiers have shot dead three Palestinian gunmen who opened fire on their post in the West Bank.
